title: Fantastic selection of community amenities!
posting_body: ['Text ID# 5777A to my cell for more info!', 'Welcome to Ribelin Ranch Apartments  in Austin, Texas!', "As a resident, you'll enjoy our beautiful one, two, and three bedroom apartments, along with a fantastic selection of community amenities.", 'All of our floorplans offer spacious living areas, a fully-equipped kitchen with tile backsplash and granite countertops, walk-in closets, an in-home washer and dryer, garden soaking tubs, built-in desk with USB outlets, built-in bookcase, and a private patio or balcony!', 'Select units also include an attached garage.', "At Ribelin Ranch Apartments, you'll experience an array of upscale amenities.", 'Relax at our resort-style swimming pool, hang out with friends in the volleyball pool or at a WiFi-enabled poolside cabana, or play fetch with your furry friend at our on-site dog park.', "We know you'll also love our 24-hour fitness center, clubhouse with a business center and gourmet coffee bar, poolside lounge area with BBQ grills, 24-hour package system, and valet trash service.", 'Choose the floorplan that fits your lifestyle and take a walkthrough video tour, or call our friendly leasing staff to schedule a tour of your new home!']
